[32m+[m[32m## ğŸ”§ Docker Commands[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### Development[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m```bash[m
[32m+[m[32m# Start services[m
[32m+[m[32mdocker-compose up[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m# Start in background[m
[32m+[m[32mdocker-compose up -d[m
[32m+[m
